Text: Dam u YIFY.... I already have the movies ur uploading but im having to D/L them again caus ur quality is so much better than the 1s ive got.

Thank you so much YIFY Team 

A/V: 10

Sadly this YIFY team comes in different flavors. Don't download any BOKUTOX rip unless you don't care about losing the audio in the middle of the end credits. Sometimes I don't care that much, as in the other three parts of this series, but this was a nice ending song, and so was the second song in the end credits of The Girl Next Door (2004), which the BOKUTOX rip also discarded.
